OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAfghanistan's Taliban ban  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flong-distance road trips   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffor solo women             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Taliban have said Afghan women     
OL,6, seeking to travel long distances by    
OL,7, road should be offered transport only  
OL,8, if accompanied by a male relative.     
OL,10,FThe directive, issued on Sunday, is the
OL,11,Flatest curb on women's rights since the
OL,12,FIslamist group seized power in August. 
OL,14,FThe majority of secondary schools      
OL,15,Fremains shut for girls, while most     
OL,16,Fwomen have been banned from working.   
OL,18,FCampaign group Human Rights Watch said 
OL,19,Fthe new restriction moved further      
OL,20,Ftowards making women prisoners.        
